Arguments: $ARGUMENTS

## Your job

Convert the request into a structured product/UI intent document.

## Must include

- product type
- primary user
- main jobs to be done
- risk level
- interaction density
- tone
- key constraints
- avoid_styles
- preferred_styles
- accessibility expectations
- responsive expectations

## Rules

