</file>

<file path=".claude/commands/ui-build.md">
Build or update implementation from approved stage specs.

Arguments: $ARGUMENTS

## Required inputs

- IntentSpec
- LayoutSpec
- TokenSpec
- ComponentSpec, if present

## Output targets

- React + TypeScript
- token-driven styling
